{"tid":467721,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇戲前面有對正長腿，好撚正 （無圖）","createTime":"2017-11-13T17:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T18:23:19.000Z","uid":20601,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f722c011e24b964065290b283ab284405971f849","tid":467721,"uid":20601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T17:50:15.000Z","msg":"屌你老母！睇你就睇啦，係要放對死人爛閪臭腳係前面張櫈到，仲要係度磨下磨下，你對腳係咪生野，好好地坐係到唔撚得既，係要放上去，有冇諗過下一個坐係到既人既感受，聞撚住你對臭閪腳味，聞足個幾倆個鐘呀！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我屌你老母死廢老！<br />\n<br />\n點知過多陣，真係有對情侶坐係到，條死廢老縮都縮唔切，屌你，我以為佢見到有人坐係前面佢會收斂下啦，屌！跟著佢順住個勢，將對腳再放係其他櫈到。如果呢對情侶有上連登既，你地就會知道啲味係邊到黎，真係鄧你哋唔抵。<br />\n<br />\n好心啦，咁大個人就自律下，比啲公德心，真唔可以怪咁多人屌你地班廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/014936_004fd458ab1692991616aca21bc3b6ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F014936_004fd458ab1692991616aca21bc3b6ef.jpg&h=352a3331&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/014938_6ced5d833159aaed16a513af3c9f2490.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F014938_6ced5d833159aaed16a513af3c9f2490.jpg&h=625fde0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fefda6f01cf362a0fdf037023d32d55b4f8ec11","tid":467721,"uid":20601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T18:20:47.000Z","msg":"正評 ： 屌化佢，屌到佢唔敢入戲院<br />\n負評 ： 事但啦，又唔係臭到我"},{"pid":"89a81b3d3527afed8ed83ada5ab82345c9adbfdf","tid":467721,"uid":58140,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T18:22:12.000Z","msg":"投你老母票咩<br />\n又唔敢當面屌柒佢 <br />\n佢廢老你咪廢柴囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b8562b2e0ea099c59865e47dc0b